OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPartly cloudy to start the day,
OL,6,Fbut the cloud clears to give away to a
OL,7,Fvery warm, or hot day for most with
OL,8,Fprolonged sunny spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA settled and mostly clear
OL,11,Fnight with the wind remaining light.
OL,12,FMild in urban areas, cooler in rural
OL,13,Fspots allowing patchy fog or mist to
OL,14,Fform in places.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FAnother hot day with
OL,17,Ftemperatures continuing to rise. Dry
OL,18,Fand sunny with the wind remaining
OL,19,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
