OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fand sunny with light winds on Monday
OL,7,Fand Tuesday. Staying hot on Monday and
OL,8,FTuesday with temperatures starting to
OL,9,Ffall by Wednesday.
